==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪbəl|-eɪbəl]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A small [[ticket]] or [[sign]] giving information about something to which it is attached or to intended to be attached.
# A [[name]] given to something or someone to categorise them as part of a particular social group.
# A [[company]] that sells [[record]]s.

====Synonyms====
*(''small ticket''): [[sign]], [[tag]], [[ticket]]
*(''name given to something or someone''): [[category]], [[pigeonhole]]

